commit message: Only update auto-version in release builds
add feedback when changing the vibrate duration preference slider
Add Esc and Settings to Tab key long-press in compact 5-row layout

Add Meta key (aka Command, Windows key)

The existing Alt key was previously setting the META key state for the generated
keys, change this to the ALT modifier.
Set targetSdkVersion to 19 to fix permission warnings.

Fix voice (microphone) key in compact 5-row layout

Also add the missing question mark in the popup when microphone is on
the main keyboard.

Switch to modern voice typing, remove now-obsolete RECORD_AUDIO permission.

http://android-developers.blogspot.com/2011/12/add-voice-typing-to-your-ime.html
has details, including the download link for the jar file that is needed
if you are building from source.

Disable ContactsDictionary, remove Contacts permission

I'm now convinced that the contacts autocomplete dictionary is more trouble
than it's worth. It requires a suspicious-looking permission, and uses
a ton of memory in some configurations, i.e. if you have a corporate account
synced.

If people feel strongly about this functionality, it should be possible to
write a separate app or service that syncs contact names to the user dictionary.

Add my (Burmese, ?????) 4-row and 5-row layouts.

Contributed by Aung Myo, thank you!

Note that the keyboard does not supply fonts. If your device does not have
the necessary localization support, the characters will not display properly.

Added ta (Tamil, ?????) 5-row layout.

Contributed by 'Stars Soft', thank you! (And sorry about the delay merging it.)

Tweaks to Ukrainian layout:

- add ? and ? altchars

Suggested by Rostyslav Sambuk-Nagornyi, thank you!

Add hu (Hungarian, Magyar) 4-row and 5-row layouts, qwertz + qwerty.
